
Class A:
Range: 0-127
Fixed bit = 0
Net bits = 8
Host bits = 24

Available/new net bits = net bits - number of fixed bit = 8-1 = 7
Total network addresses = 2^7 = 128
total host addresses = 2^24 = 16777216
total available host addresses = 2^24 -2 = 16777216-2 = 16777214

Total addresses = 128*16777214 = 2147483392

