Class B: 

Range :128-191
Fixed bits= 10
Net bits= 16
Host bits= 16
Available net bits=net bits-number of fixed bits= 16-2 = 14
Total network address = 2^14 =16384
Total host address = 2^16 =65536
Total available host address = 2^16 - 2 =65534
Total address = 16384*65534 =1073709056

Class C: 

Range :192-223
Fixed bits= 110
Net bits= 24
Host bits= 8
Available net bits=net bits-number of fixed bits= 24-3 = 21
Total network address = 2^21 =2097152
Total host address = 2^8 =256
Total available host address = 2^8 - 2 = 254
Total address = 2097152*254= 532676608 




